# **09  Product risks**

| **Risk** | **Likelihood** | **Impact** | **Mitigation** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **Dish database incomplete at launch** | High | Critical | Phase gate: launch only after 500 dishes tagged and validated. No shortcuts. |
| **Cold-start plan quality fails Day 0** | Medium | High | RE v1 must use class-first pipeline. Unit test cold-start paths for all 5 cohorts. |
| **Onboarding drop-off ****>**** 30%** | Medium | High | Test each screen independently. Cut any screen with > 30% drop-off. |
| **Hard constraint violation (diet/allergen)** | Low | Critical | SQL safety-gate queries after every RE change. Must return 0 violations. |
| **App store rejection** | Medium | High | Review Apple/Google guidelines before submission. No health claims without medical disclaimer. |

